text: Hugues Landon (born 26 June 1930) is a French equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Living people Category:French male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of France Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
